  "original_title": "\u0da2\u0db4\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dba\u0dda \u0dbb\u0dd0\u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dcf \u0dc3\u0db3\u0dc4\u0dcf 22\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db4\u0dd2\u0da7\u0dad\u0dca\u0dc0 \u0dba\u0dad\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "22 are leaving for jobs in Japan",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Sri Lanka Foreign Employment Bureau and the IM Japan Institute jointly offered air tickets for 22 workers who are going to leave for work in Japan under the program of providing free jobs to Sri Lankans in Japan today (20th) at the same bureau.",
        "Under this, 14 youths have qualified for jobs in the construction sector and 8 youths for jobs in the nursing sector.",
        "Bureau Chairman Major General Mahinda Hathurusingha, General Manager DDP Senanayake, IM Japan Director M. Kome, IM Japan's new local director Tamura and others were present for the air ticket awarding ceremony."
      ],
